regulations gave this account 
amal forces with armored personnel carriers and 106mm recoilless 
artillery advanced across nabatiyehs main street to the towns old 
sector where hezbollah fighters were installed in sniping nests 
the fighting in nabatiyeh is ferocious rescue teams have not 
been able to evacuate casualties in some parts of the town 
nabatiyeh citizens have been hiding in basements and bomb shelters 
since tuesday 
