officials on tuesday hustled him onto a plane to the dominican 
republic without a passport us law enforcement sources said 
dominican republic officials put matta on a new yorkbound 
flight and he was arrested aboard the jetliner by us marshals 
the sources said 
angry honduran legislators labeled mattas capture a 
kidnapping and the honduran foreign ministry began an 
investigation of the procedures used the honduran constitution 
prohibits extradition of honduran citizens to the united states 
matta was kidnapped in open violation of our laws carlos 
montoya speaker of honduras singlehouse legislature told 
