roxane laboratories in columbus ohio gives a drug to poor 
terminal cancer patients in severe pain said company spokesman 
gerald c wojta the company announced its plan several years ago 
wyeth laboratories a division of american home products corp 
has a compassionate program for the tryly needy through the 
physician said spokeswoman audrey ashby its judged on a 
patientbypatient basis 
searle is a researchbased company that develops manufactures 
and markets prescription pharmaceuticals worldwide it is a wholly 
owned subsidiary of monsanto co 
